<P>
Column; Brief 
</P>
</TYPE>
</DOC>
<DOC>
<DOCNO> LA042490-0009 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 208641 </DOCID>
<DATE>
<P>
April 24, 1990, Tuesday, Valley Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Metro; Part B; Page 3; Column 1 
