HNB Financial Group: The Huntington Beach-based parent company of Huntington 
National Bank reported earnings of $335,000 for the first quarter, up 50% from 
earnings of $223,000 in the year-earlier period. Total assets at the end of 
March were nearly $121 million, up 54% from the $78.6 million reported for the 
comparable period in 1989. 
