OFFICIAL VISITS; AMERICAN NEWSPAPER PUBLISHERS ASSOCIATION; KIDNAPINGS -- 
MEXICO; DRUG ARRESTS -- TEXAS; MURDERS -- MEXICO; CAMARENA, ENRIQUE; DRUG 
ENFORCEMENT OFFICERS; ALVAREZ MACHAIN, HUMBERTO; MEDICAL CARE -- MEXICO; HEALTH 
INSURANCE; EMPLOYEE BENEFITS; FOREIGN LABOR; UNITED FARM WORKERS OF AMERICA; 
CHAVEZ, CESAR 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
