WAXING RELIGIOUS: Not all the attractions developed by Allen Parkinson, founder 
of Movieland Wax Museum who hopes to create a "Life of Christ" wax museum in 
Anaheim (D1), have survived. . . . An earlier Buena Park creation, the Japanese 
Village and Deer Park, went belly up (and antlers down) four years after 
