-- UNITED STATES; FISHING INDUSTRY -- EUROPE; STAR KIST FOODS INC; 
ENVIRONMENTALISTS; GREENPEACE; DOLPHIN COALITION; CONSERVATION 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
